Description: Provides efficient and scalable implementations of class imbalance
    handling techniques for binary classification within the tidymodels framework.
    The package introduces custom recipe steps designed to improve predictive
    performance in imbalanced datasets by combining over-sampling and
    under-sampling strategies. The methods are grounded in recent research on
    churn prediction in retail banking and are optimized for performance and
    auditability.
